channel.title: [REL] A bunch of 07 models (3rd age weapons, Trident of the seas, And more)
channel.description:
Hey all. Figured I'd dump some of the newer RS07 models. These are just some of what I have, I haven't sorted all the newer ones or whatnot.
The full directory can be found [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/]here[/url].
3rd Age bow: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/3rd_age_bow.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140613045817/2007scape/images/2/2d/3rd_age_bow_equipped.png[/img]
3rd Age wand: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/3rd_age_wand.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140714024054/2007scape/images/4/4a/3rd_age_mage_armour_equipped.png[/img]
3rd Age sword: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/3rd_age_sword.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140613054420/2007scape/images/6/63/3rd_age_longsword_equipped.png[/img]
3rd Age cloak/cape: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/3rd_age_cape.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV3bG/29567f475c.png[/img]
Abyssal Tentacle: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/Abyssal_Tentacle.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140504173522/2007scape/images/3/3c/Abyssal_tentacle_equipped.png[/img]
Partyhat and specs: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/Partyhat_and_specs.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140613054419/2007scape/images/3/3e/Partyhat_%26_specs_equipped.png[/img]
Trident of the seas: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/Trident_of_the_Seas.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140130173105/2007scape/images/f/f8/Trident_of_the_seas_equipped.png[/img]
Wilderness rings: (all 3) [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/Wildy_Rings.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV3AH/e69e7eb44f.jpg[/img][img]http://puu.sh/aV3Bo/81e2dfdfdb.jpg[/img][img]http://puu.sh/aV3BY/90dba93fd1.jpg[/img]
Goblin mask: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/goblin_mask.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140613031858/2007scape/images/a/a0/Goblin_mask_equipped.png[/img]
Imp mask: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/imp_mask.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://img3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140613031959/2007scape/images/2/25/Imp_mask_equipped.png[/img]
[b]The following items I found, but they do not seem to have names (I did a poor search on them). If you know their real name, please let me know.[/b]
Unknown scimitar: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/unknown_scimitar.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV3U1/cc36b2621e.jpg[/img]
Unknown sword: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/unknown_sword.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV41p/ff0cb4a298.jpg[/img]
Unknown trident: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/unknown_trident.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV43T/0329f1651b.png[/img]
[b]I believe this one is the [url=http://2007.runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Smoke_battlestaff]Smoke battlestaff[/url] but it's not colored like on the wiki.[/b] Unknown staff: [url=http://rsps.canyourcode.com/RS07Models/unknown_staff.zip]Download[/url] [img]http://puu.sh/aV48x/798f2db213.jpg[/img]
